### SHOWCASE: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8L3seFObMa0

  A fully performance-focused overlay for your gameplay, designed primarily for competitive PvP, with utilities for redstone, grinding, and other useful features to enhance a more competitive experience. It keeps your game visually clean while preserving the vanilla look, and can be combined with any other texture packs of your choice without interfering with their visuals when layered on top.

If you enjoy using my texture pack and would like to support me, please consider favoriting the project!! It really helps give my work more visibility and improves the experience for other players. Luv u guys!!!! ❤️

# Current gameplay tweaks:

### PVP:
- Low fire (screen and block models);
- Low shield;
- Small totem pop;
- No explosion, smoke and effect particles;
- Cleaner damage, totem pop and sweep hit particles;
- Enchantment icons and colors;
- Cleaner underwater screen;
- Transparent water;
- No fishing hook;
- Dark-mode GUI (no inventory included);
- Clean rain and snowing textures.

### Vannila Utils:
- Visual Powered Snow;
- Visual Note Block notes;
- Visual full grown crops and amethyst;
- Visual dispenser, observer and hopper's directions;
- Visual redstone power levels;
- Visual caldroon and composter levels;
- Outlined ores
- Visual Suspicious Gravel and Sand;
- Custom font;
- Fullbright (Only on Optifine);
- Quieter pistons, villagers, thunders, minecarts, underwater sounds, dispensers and rain.

